## perceval-mozilla 0.3.16 - (2023-10-20)

**Dependencies updateds:**

 * Add Python 3.10 and 3.11 and drop 3.7 support\
   Python 3.7 reached the end of life phase on June 27 2023 and is no
   longer supported.


